                <p style="margin: 0 0 0.6rem 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 0.8rem;">
                  Complete list of all cases for this scenario with full environment details.
                </p>
                <div style="overflow-x: auto;">
                  <table
                    style="
                      width: 100%;
